227
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:37,680
I don't think there are control rods.

228
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,350
I don't think there's a core.

229
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:43,390
No, you're... You're mistaken.

230
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,640
Akimov said.

231
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:04,390
Let's go.

232
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:19,060
<font color="#ff00ff">(MISHA WAILING)</font>:{\c} No!

233
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:22,890
- <font color="#ff00ff">(MISHA SCREAMING)</font>
- Ignatenko, get on his hose!

234
00:19:22,890 --> 00:19:24,810
It's all right. Breathe.

235
00:19:24,810 --> 00:19:26,560
- <font color="#ff00ff">(MISHA WHIMPERING)</font>
- Misha.

236
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:28,560
All right, all right. Easy, Misha.

237
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:34,260
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS)</font>

238
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:36,390
<font color="#ff00ff">(GROANING)</font>

239
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:53,600
<font color="#ffff00">♪ </font><font color="#ffff00">♪</font>

240
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:59,640
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARMS BUZZING)</font>

241
00:20:05,430 --> 00:20:07,270
Are you sure?

242
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:10,060
Akimov...

243
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:16,730
- <font color="#ff00ff">(MEN GRUNTING)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(METAL SCRAPING)</font>

244
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:24,970
Move.

245
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:34,020
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

246
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:36,970
Come on, go!

247
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:42,140
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS, SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY)</font>

